name: Tarsal
all_locations: New York, NY, USA; San Francisco, CA, USA; Remote
long_description: Tarsal is a data pipeline custom built for security teams. As security data grows 25% year over year, security teams desperately need access to best-in-class data infrastructure. Tarsal bridges the gap between the modern data stack and security teams, pioneering the modern security data stack.
one_liner: Data pipeline for your security data lake.
